<div class="container">
  <div class="message-container">
    <div class="messages">
      <h2>Do you have an instrument<br>you don't use anymore?</h2>
      <h3>Why not <strong>share</strong> with others and <strong>earn</strong> profit from your unused instrument?</h3>
